@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ryrllo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.76)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.06) - (v1 + 0.16 * v2 + 0.36)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(tmp) - wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = ((v0 - (tmp + 0.59 + tmp + 0.50)) * wp.cos((v0 + 0.59 / v1 + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
